Package: hyprneko
Architecture: linux-any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Wayland-native desktop pet (Hyprland-first)
 Hyprneko is a Wayland-native desktop pet inspired by oneko. It runs as a
 wlr-layer-shell overlay and chases the global cursor by polling Hyprland's
 IPC socket — no X11/XWayland involved. Includes an optional Pomodoro mode
 and a Waybar custom-module integration.
